descp2: A string, one of `channels_last` (default) or `channels_first`. The ordering of the dimensions in the inputs.`channels_last` corresponds to inputs with shape`(batch, height, width, channels)` while `channels_first`corresponds to inputs with shape`(batch, channels, height, width)`. It defaults to the `image_data_format` value found in your Keras config file at `~/.keras/keras.json`. If you never set it, then it will be 'channels_last'.
